PN,30501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FAn AI video advert for a "smart
OL,8,Frobotic puppy" which claims to be
OL,9,Fcapable of sitting on command and
OL,10,Fresponding to its owner's voice has
OL,11,Fbeen ruled "misleading" by the
OL,12,Fadvertising watchdog.
OL,14,FITV News has uncovered a number of
OL,15,Fsimilar social media posts for
OL,16,Fdifferent products, which use
OL,17,Felaborate AI videos and pictures
OL,18,Fpromising high quality items - only
OL,19,Ffor the real thing to look very
OL,20,Fdifferent.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@NO]sD@LOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FWe found AI-generated images and
OL,8,Fvideos on social media promoting the
OL,9,Fproduct, known online as "Wuffy",
OL,10,F"Wiggy" or "Waggy", all promising a
OL,11,Fhigh-tech toy which behaves like a
OL,12,Freal dog.
OL,14,FThe videos use AI animation to give
OL,15,Fthe toy a realistic look, with one
OL,16,Fvideo showing the toy walking out of
OL,17,Fthe packaging with the kind of motion
OL,18,Fyou'd associate with a real puppy.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUqD@`O]rD@AOUrD@GO]rD@LOUrD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FBut customers have been left
OL,8,Fdisappointed when what arrives turns
OL,9,Fout to be a cheap toy - with none of
OL,10,Fthe advanced features promised by the
OL,11,Fvideos online.
OL,13,FLaura Merriman, from Rhondda Cynon
OL,14,FTaff, ordered two Wuffy dogs priced at
OL,15,F#12.99 from TikTok Shop after seeing
OL,16,Fan video advert on the app.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,F"They were advertising these robotic
OL,8,Fdogs walking, barking at the kids,
OL,9,Finteracting with them. I thought,
OL,10,Fthese are perfect, this is exactly
OL,11,Fwhat I want," she said.
OL,13,FWhen the products arrived, she was
OL,14,Fshocked by the reality.
OL,16,F"They were not even the same colour,
OL,17,Fnot the same shape, everything was
OL,18,Fcompletely different," she said. "It
OL,19,Fwas very disappointing. These weren't
OL,20,Fthe AI robotic dogs that I thought
OL,21,Fthey could have been."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@MO]xD@AOUzD@VO]zD@bOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FAfter finding a number of complaints
OL,8,Fabout the quality of the product
OL,9,Fonline, we bought it from TikTok Shop
OL,10,F- and found out for ourselves why
OL,11,Fcustomers felt so let down.
OL,13,FWuffy didn't behave like a real puppy,
OL,14,For respond to voice commands. All it
OL,15,Fcould do was move backwards and
OL,16,Fforwards, and squeak.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FLaura was refunded, but ITV News has
OL,8,Fspoken to customers who bought the
OL,9,Fproduct from different websites who
OL,10,Fare still trying to get their money
OL,11,Fback.
OL,13,FThe Wuffy video banned by the
OL,14,FAdvertising Standards Authority (ASA)
OL,15,Fwas a paid-for advert hosted on
OL,16,FFacebook, after a number of complaints
OL,17,Ftriggered an investigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FJessica Tye, Regulatory Projects
OL,8,FManager at the ASA, told us: "The
OL,9,Fcompany was advertising this product
OL,10,Fin a way that was completely
OL,11,Fmisleading to people, and it's
OL,12,Funderstandable that people who bought
OL,13,Fthis toy were hugely disappointed."
OL,15,FAI is being used in advertising by a
OL,16,Fnumber of well-established brands, as
OL,17,Fthe software can be used to enhance
OL,18,Fbackgrounds and create artificial
OL,19,Ffashion models.
OL,26,@pD@^OUuD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FBut developments in AI are making it
OL,8,Fharder for consumers to spot that the
OL,9,Ftechnology has been used at all - and
OL,10,Fare making it easier for misleading
OL,11,Fcontent to be created.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FThe CAP code followed by the ASA
OL,8,Fcontains no specific regulation on the
OL,9,Fuse of AI in adverts, and there is no
OL,10,Frequirement for advertisers to
OL,11,Fdisclose when AI has been used.
OL,13,FBut the code does state that whether
OL,14,FAI is used or not, adverts cannot be
OL,15,Fmisleading about what a product looks
OL,16,Flike, or its features.
OL,18,FSocial media companies like Meta and
OL,19,FTikTok have their own self-imposed
OL,20,Frules about labelling AI content
OL,21,Fonline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FTikTok requires all AI content to be
OL,8,Flabelled. Meta uses tools to detect
OL,9,Fwhere AI has been used and requires
OL,10,Flabelling of some content.
OL,12,FWhen asked whether using AI on adverts
OL,13,Ffor products should be more tightly
OL,14,Fregulated, Jessica said: "Our codes
OL,15,Fare really clear that ads must not
OL,16,Fmislead, and we find that principle-
OL,17,Fbased approach is really effective
OL,18,Fbecause it means we can be really
OL,19,Fflexible when new technology emerges.
OL,26,@vD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,F"This investigation demonstrates that
OL,8,Four existing rules are fit for
OL,9,Fpurpose. We don't need AI-specific
OL,10,Frules to find that these ads were
OL,11,Fmisleading and in breach, but we are
OL,12,Fproducing new guidance all the time to
OL,13,Faddress new techniques being used."
OL,15,FTracy Ives, from Suffolk, believes
OL,16,Fsocial media companies need to do more
OL,17,Fto tackle the use of AI in content
OL,18,Fused to promote products online, after
OL,19,Fbeing duped by an AI image of a lamp.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FShe bought what she thought was a hand-
OL,8,Fmade stained glass lamp from a small
OL,9,Fbusiness based in Cambridge - only to
OL,10,Freceive a substandard version of the
OL,11,Fproduct which looked very different
OL,12,Fwhen it arrived.
OL,14,FWhen she complained to the retailer,
OL,15,Fshe was reassured the item was
OL,16,Fhandmade, and offered 15% off her next
OL,17,Forder.
OL,19,FThe advert has since been removed from
OL,20,FFacebook - but Tracy said it has had a
OL,21,Flasting impact.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,F"I don't trust a lot of things I see
OL,8,Fon the internet now," she said. "I
OL,9,Fthink AI can be very dangerous, it's
OL,10,Fonly going to get worse."
OL,12,FShe told us social media platforms
OL,13,Fneed to do more to crack down on AI
OL,14,Fcontent which misleads customers about
OL,15,Fitems for sale online.
OL,17,F"They've got responsibility as they
OL,18,Flet the businesses advertise on their
OL,19,Fplatform, so they need to do more,"
OL,20,Fshe said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@UO]pD@aOUrD@YO]yD@AOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FA spokesperson for Meta said: "We
OL,8,Fdon't allow ads that use deceptive or
OL,9,Fmisleading practices and have removed
OL,10,Fthis advertiser from our platforms for
OL,11,Fviolating our Advertising Standards,
OL,12,Fwhich apply to all ads on our
OL,13,Fplatforms regardless of whether they
OL,14,Ffeature AI-generated content or not."
OL,16,FMeta has removed the advertiser and
OL,17,Fassociated content from Facebook.
OL,26,@oD@_OUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FAccording to TikTok, sellers on TikTok
OL,8,FShop are provided with guidance to
OL,9,Favoid the inappropriate use of AI, and
OL,10,Fall AI content on the platform must be
OL,11,Flabelled.
OL,13,FThe platform had previously removed
OL,14,Fthe listing for the Wuffy products
OL,15,Fordered by ITV News.
OL,17,FITV News has reached out to the
OL,18,Fcompany behind the Wuffy product but
OL,19,Fhas not received a response.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
