FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774545075
OL,3,C'Robot puppy' Facebook ad banned as
OL,4,Ccustomers report being misled by AI
OL,5,Ccontent
OL,7,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,8,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,9,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,10,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,11,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,12,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/16
